cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on natural language processing tasks such as machine translation, automatic speech recognition, and spoken language translation. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is also likely as the dataset includes instructional videos and the paper discusses multimodal summarization. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper deals with multimodal data (videos with subtitles and translations). 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper presents integrated sequence-to-sequence baselines for various tasks. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a possible category as the paper deals with natural language understanding and multimodal data, which are both relevant to AI research.
